; Regression test for issue #583: --monthly prices report SUM rather than average or end of month price (BZ#583)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/583
;
; When using 'prices' with --monthly (-M), ledger incorrectly sums prices
; within a month instead of showing the average or end-of-month price.
; January has two prices ($500.00 and $510.00); the sum $1,010.00 is shown,
; but the correct behavior would be $510.00 (end-of-month) or $505.00 (average).

commodity $
    format $1,000.00

2013/01/05 Buy stock
    Assets:Investments   10 AAPL @ $500.00
    Assets:Cash

2013/01/12 Buy more
    Assets:Investments   10 AAPL @ $510.00
    Assets:Cash

2013/02/05 Buy again
    Assets:Investments   10 AAPL @ $520.00
    Assets:Cash

test -M prices
2013/01/01 AAPL        $1,010.00
2013/02/01 AAPL          $520.00
end test
